description:
Armin Van Buuren - A STATE OF TRANCE (2014)


Consisting of two sets from the Dutch DJ and producer -- one is dubbed "On the Beach" while the other, slightly darker and sleeker set is dubbed "In the Club" -- A State of Trance 2014 provides another annual assortment of whirlwind trance from Armin van Buuren. Featuring selections from the likes of Jorn van Deynhoven, Gareth Emery, Orjan Nilsen, and Aly & Fila, among others, the package concludes with van Buuren's own March 2014 single, "Ping Pong," a gimmicky but clever track that should remain one of his more notable productions.
